column3: Director of Law and Technology, [Community Legal Services Philadelphia](https://clsphila.org)

Innovator in Residence at the [Future of the Profession Initiative (“FPI”)](https://www.law.upenn.edu/futureprofessioninitiative/), University of Pennsylvania’s Carey School of Law. Concurrently Executive Director of [Access to Justice Tech Fellows (“A2J Tech Fellows”)](https://www.atjtechfellows.org)
[Seattle Social Justice Hackathon](https://ssjhackathon.devpost.com) & Head of Design at [Stemma.ai](https://www.stemma.ai/about)

Inaugural Exec. Director of [Temple University Institute for Law, Innovation & Technology, Temple University’s Beasley School of Law](https://law.temple.edu/ilit/?_ga=2.128729804.1728086540.1663436415-1329402727.1663436415)
